// Kodex Topic Graph
// Visualizes Kodex topic relationships as a Mermaid flowchart.
// Fetches all topics with content, builds graph edges from 'related' fields,
// and renders an interactive Mermaid diagram where clicking a node navigates to that topic.

FUNCTION Graph()                                                        EXPORT
  CALLS: listTopicsWithContent (kodex-api), buildGraphEdges (graph-utils), generateMermaidGraph (graph-utils)
  Read selectedProject from kodexStore.
  On mount (or project change):
    1. Fetch all topics with content via kodexApi.listTopicsWithContent.
    2. Build edges from each topic's 'related' field using buildGraphEdges.
    3. Generate Mermaid graph syntax using generateMermaidGraph.
    4. Store the Mermaid source in state.
  Render a DiagramEmbed with the Mermaid source.
  On node click (handleNodeClick): navigate to /kodex/topics/:nodeId.
